data.description: Spacious 2 story 4 bedroom, 3 bath with a Flex or game room in sought after Grapevine Colleyville ISD home. With an open concept kitchen that is big enough for multiple chefs while the two living areas are great for those big get togethers.  With 2 bedrooms down and the sizable primary suite will provide you privacy & relaxation you desire. The second floor has 2 bedrooms, with an additional flex space, media or game room. Beat the next Texas heat wave with this gorgeous pool & spa and backyard oasis providing shade with a covered patio. Zoned for award winning Bransford elementary school and is close to shopping and dining. Come see this beautiful home that awaits for you. Roof 2000, water heater 2018, HVAC was replaced in 2014 and has a warranty until July of 2024 but can be extended.
